    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 A Solid, Well-Kept Car \u2014 Honestly Priced for Real Value!\n\nThis vehicle is in good condition, and we're proud to say it! It starts up reliably, drives smoothly, and has clearly been taken care of over the years. You'll find the interior is clean and comfortable, the mechanicals are in good working order, and it handles everyday driving with ease. There are minor signs of normal wear \u2014 nothing unexpected for a car of its age \u2014 but nothing that gets in the way of a great ownership experience. If you're looking for a dependable ride that won't let you down, this one deserves a serious look. Come take it for a spin \u2014 we think you'll be impressed!",
      "price": 31000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 29
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This exceptional vehicle is offered in mint condition at $47,500 \u2014 a rare find in the used car market that truly lives up to the designation. The exterior is immaculate, with absolutely no scratches, dents, chips, or paint imperfections of any kind; the finish retains a deep, showroom-quality shine that turns heads. The interior is equally pristine \u2014 all upholstery, trim panels, and surfaces are spotless, with no fading, cracking, staining, or wear evident anywhere in the cabin. Mechanically, the vehicle is in outstanding shape: the engine runs smoothly and quietly, all systems function exactly as intended, and there are no warning lights, unusual noises, or known issues. This is a car that has been exceptionally well maintained and treated with great care throughout its life, and it shows in every detail. A pre-purchase inspection is welcomed and encouraged \u2014 we are confident it will confirm everything described here.",
      "price": 47500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 29
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in mint condition \u2014 an exceptional find for buyers who want a car that looks and drives as though it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior is flawless, with absolutely no scratches, dents, or paint imperfections \u2014 the finish retains a deep, glossy shine throughout. The interior is equally immaculate, with pristine upholstery, spotless carpeting, and all trim pieces in perfect, undamaged condition. Every mechanical system functions exactly as intended, with no warning lights, no unusual noises, and a smooth, responsive driving experience. The vehicle has been meticulously maintained, with a full service history, and shows no signs of neglect or hard use. All electronics, climate controls, and safety features operate flawlessly. This is a rare opportunity to purchase a vehicle that truly requires nothing \u2014 simply drive it and enjoy.",
      "price": 47500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 29
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
