      "description": "Meet the one that sets the standard. This stunning beauty has been cherished from day one \u2014 every surface gleaming, every detail attended to with the kind of care most cars only dream of. Slide into the cabin and you're greeted by an interior that feels lifted straight from the showroom floor: supple materials, crisp controls, and that unmistakable scent of a car that has been truly loved. Under the hood, she purrs with quiet confidence, ready to carry you into your next chapter without a single hesitation. This isn't just a car \u2014 it's a statement that some things only get better with intention. Opportunities like this don't linger.",
      "price": 46000.0,
